Over 300 shotgun barrels (some new).Most brands: mostly Remington, Browning, Mossberg & Winchester. Many have been refurbished, bores honed to shinny bright, some reblued/refinished. Different lengths, chokes, some screw-in chokes, vent rib & plain.;
Average price a bit over $100. There are just too many to list here. Email for complete inventory.
